name: My Window #19
description:
Some days I feel that I don´t feel enough 
I would like to don´t to need to use something more to live fine
But I smoke to do something with my time, to go farther, to feel.

My life behind the window
Looking at the sunsets crossing up there
And my life in the same city

I love my life here, last year was really wonderful
But nothing like looking at something different every day.
